## Condenser Installation Note  


When installing a new condenser, add DENSO OIL9 compressor oil into the refrigeration cycle.  


Supplemental amount 30 ml (30 cc, 1.0 fl oz)  


## CONDENSER INSPECTION  


1. Inspect for cracks, damage, and oil leakage. If any are found, replace the condenser. 
2. Inspect for fins clogged by dust. If any are clogged, remove the dust from the fins.  


3. Inspect for bent fins. If any are bent, use a flathead screwdriver to straighten them.